<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٩٠٨ -<span class="c5"> حَدَّثَنَا عَمْرُو بْنُ عَاصِمٍ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا هَمَّامٌ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ قَتَادَةَ قَالَ:</span> قُلْتُ لِأَنَسٍ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَكَانَتِ الْمُصَافَحَةُ فِي أَصْحَابِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> نَعَمْ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>